# git-crypt — encrypt third-party audio assets at rest in the public repo.
#
# The OGG below is Sound Ideas SFX library content licensed for end-product
# use only; its EULA disallows redistribution of the raw asset. git-crypt
# encrypts it with AES-256 using a symmetric key held in 1Password and stored
# as the GIT_CRYPT_KEY GitHub Actions secret. Cloners without the key see an
# encrypted blob; CI decrypts before `./gradlew build` so release jars carry
# the audio. See BUILD.md for the dev-machine unlock procedure.
src/main/resources/assets/dungeontrain/sounds/train_engine.ogg filter=git-crypt diff=git-crypt
